
                            [help boards]
-----------------------===========+=========-----------------------

Usage: boards [list || view || read || post || remove] [board number] [post number || subject]

boards list
  List boards

boards view [board number]
  View headers of posts on board [board number]

boards read [board number] [post number]
  Read post [post number] on board [board number].
  If no [post number] is given, reads the next unread note.

boards post [board number] [subject]
  Create a new note on [board number] with subject [subject].

board remove [board number] [post number]
  Remove post number [post number] from board [board number].

